                <li><p> Complete <alert>4</alert> checkpoints. </p></li>
                <li><p> Add <alert>5</alert> items to your prep work book. </p></li>
                <li><p> Write solutions to all assigned problems in <alert>Homework 4</alert> </p></li>
                <li><p> Finish any remaining work on <alert>Activity 3</alert>. </p></li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </subsection>
        
</section>
